{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/return-a-sorted-array-without-changing-the-original-array","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"functional-programming","demoType":null,"title":"Vratite obrađeni podudni red bez menjanja izvornog reda podataka","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Jedan efekat metode <code>sort</code> je što menja redos elemenata u originalnom nizu podataka. Drugim rečima, menja niz podataka na mestu. Jedan način da se to izbegne je prvo konkatere prazan niz podataka sa onim koji se sortira (zapamtite da <code>slice</code> i <code>concat</code> vraćaju novi niz podataka), a zatim koristite metodu <code>sort</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d7da9367417b2b2512b6a","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Koristi putanju <code>sort</code> u funkciji <code>nonMutatingSort</code> za sortiranje elemenata niza podataka po rastućem redosledu. Funkcija treba da vrati novi niz podataka, a ne da promeni vrednost <code>globalArray</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301237,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/return-a-sorted-array-without-changing-the-original-array"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"const globalArray = [5, 6, 3, 2, 9];\r\n\r\nfunction nonMutatingSort(arr) {\r\n  // Only change code below this line\r\n\r\n\r\n  // Only change code above this line\r\n}\r\n\r\nnonMutatingSort(globalArray);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vaš kod treba da koristi metodu <code>sort</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(nonMutatingSort.toString().match(/\\.sort/g));"},{"text":"<p>Vrednost <code>globalArray</code> ne bi trebalo da se menja.</p>","testString":"assert(JSON.stringify(globalArray) === JSON.stringify([5, 6, 3, 2, 9]));"},{"text":"<p><code>nonMutatingSort(globalArray)</code> treba da vrati <code>[2, 3, 5, 6, 9]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(\r\n  JSON.stringify(nonMutatingSort(globalArray)) ===\r\n    JSON.stringify([2, 3, 5, 6, 9])\r\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>nonMutatingSort(globalArray)</code> Ne sme biti ugrađeni kod.</p>","testString":"assert(!nonMutatingSort.toString().match(/\\[.*?[23569].*?\\]/gs));"},{"text":"<p>Funkcija treba da vrati novi red podataka, a ne prosleđeni red podataka.</p>","testString":"assert(nonMutatingSort(globalArray) !== globalArray);"},{"text":"<p><code>nonMutatingSort([1, 30, 4, 21, 100000])</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>[1, 4, 21, 30, 100000]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(JSON.stringify(nonMutatingSort([1, 30, 4, 21, 100000])) ===\r\n    JSON.stringify([1, 4, 21, 30, 100000]))"},{"text":"<p><code>nonMutatingSort([140000, 104, 99])</code> treba da vrati <code>[99, 104, 140000]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(JSON.stringify(nonMutatingSort([140000, 104, 99])) ===\r\n    JSON.stringify([99, 104, 140000]))"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#functional-programming","dashedName":"return-a-sorted-array-without-changing-the-original-array","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"functional-programming","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/split-a-string-into-an-array-using-the-split-method","prevChallengePath"